ture still</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xlGP6OC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Messy lobby</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jrqaIJ3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dQeNEsH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uourdFL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Amusement park</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AiAq7Ix.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8sTLkOL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/unPThsy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/14nPhoO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mhTtJkL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oWKGhTW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NILAI8Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Giant mining apartment complex</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jeoHKLW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Explored for hours and maybe only saw half</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dgjwCom.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DPpzSYT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Old communal bath</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/moQH3bJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gqhVjNt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V74HGwE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jOBBzrf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p48lAVL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This place has been abandoned for 50 years</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lIcWgaZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Little guesthouse by the river</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gIhXne9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/44aZ5jW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Loved the karaoke machine</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HiSclQn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SlwygUW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Onsen hotel</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tsZEiSE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ski resort hotels</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vi6yLQB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6IGDSQa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Old apartment of the owners?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JDeVCET.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Most of them look okay from the outside</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pGxp9A0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J8ausDQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sometimes the rooms look completely untouched</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JtvPHnu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gBsbyIE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Onsen</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v45sYjx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vv8yHKd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ski lodge</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rkjLZ9c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OWNAkkV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This hotel was either untouched</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/S5JtZyo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BVl8D8Y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Or completely destroyed by the broken roof</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1pfXwTQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Often there is still food in the fridge</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p4eQj9P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Like a horror movie</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ayf7pdX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Could barely tell that it had been abandoned for so long</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9jLVhQy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Once you leave the big city in Japan there are so many abandoned homes and hotels. Usually the doors are all unlocked and you can just walk in. Still full of stuff and barely vandalized. Most have been abandoned since the 90s when the price bubble burst.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0I8FmGA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ihavenosister]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>